### Study codes
This repository contains the codes developed from my forth semester on-wards in various languages, primarily Java, python, C, C++, C#, HTML, CSS, PHP, Matlab, and maybe many more or less.

```
$ cd your_repo_root/study-codes
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout main
$ cat README.md
```

### Designer Templates
Most of the codes are part of project and work together, but some of them may be useful snippets
